The paper discusses the modelling of a society as a social network and a multi-agent system, which falls under the categories of social informatics (cs.SI), social computing (cs.SOC), and multi-agent systems (cs.MA). The use of predictive analysis and community detection also involves artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and cybersecurity (cs.CYBER) techniques.
